  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>questDescription-&gt;A s商场 irradiated creature has been captured by wasteland raiders and is being held in their camp. The local settlement is offering payment and a containment cage for its safe rescue - these creatures are valuable for research and companionship in the harsh wasteland.</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Large.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>questDescription-&gt;A massive apex predator of the wasteland has been captured by heavily fortified raiders who plan to weaponize it against their enemies. This is an extremely 危险 creature, evolved to survive in the harshest post-nuclear conditions. Successfully rescue it and you'll receive state-of-the-art containment technology capable of h老旧ing such a formidable beast.</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Large.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Large.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>任务描述-&gt;掠夺者完成了不可能的任务——他们囚禁了荒原上最可怕的掠食者之一。这个阿尔法样本代表了多年来对辐射和环境危害的进化适应。救援需要大量力量，但回报包括战前军事科学家开发的先进遏制系统。</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Large.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Large.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>任务描述-&gt;情报报告显示袭击者捕获了可能是其物种的最后一个——一个巨大的荒地庞然大物。这种生物的科学和战术价值怎么强调都不为过。发动全面的救援行动，并拥有后世界末日世界最先进的生物收容系统。</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Large.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Medium.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>任务描述-&gt; 一只中型掠食者已被装备精良的袭击者捕获，他们计划在角斗中使用它。这种生物已经很好地适应了受辐射的荒地，并且可以为任何定居点带来宝贵的补充。营救它并获得强化收容系统作为奖励。</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Medium.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Medium.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>questDescription-&gt;Raiders have caged a 危险 but valuable wasteland predator, likely planning to sell it to the highest bidder. The local authorities want this creature rescued and properly contained before it falls into the wrong hands. A military-grade cage awaits successful mercenaries.</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Medium.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Medium.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>questDescription-&gt;A formidable wasteland hunter sits trapped in a raider camp, its natural ferocity slowly being broken by captivity. Liberation of this creature would not only be a merciful act but also earn you a professional-grade containment cage - perfect for housing 危险 specimens.</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Medium.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Small.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>questDescription-&gt;A s商场 irradiated creature has been captured by wasteland raiders and is being held in their camp. The local settlement is offering payment and a containment cage for its safe rescue - these creatures are valuable for research and companionship in the harsh wasteland.</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Small.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Small.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>questDescription-&gt;Raiders have trapped a s商场 wasteland animal for their sick entertainment. Help liberate this innocent creature from their makeshift prison, and you'll be rewarded with a proper cage to keep it safe from the dangers of the post-nuclear world.</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Small.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Small.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>任务描述-&gt;一种无害的荒地生物落入了无情的掠夺者手中。当地人希望在袭击者决定将其作为下一顿大餐之前将其救出。你的奖励：一个坚固的笼子和那些在这个荒凉的世界里仍然关心生命的人的感激之情。</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueAnimal_Small.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>任务描述-&gt;来自[asker_faction_name]的绝望信号已经在无线电静电中噼啪作响。他们的一名人民，[prisoner_nameDef]，被荒地掠夺者抓获，并被关押在一座戒备森严的奴隶营中。绑架者以残暴闻名，而时间已经不多了。在这位幸存者成为严酷荒原的又一个受害者之前，发起救援行动来解救他们。</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>questDescription-&gt;Intelligence from [asker_faction_name] reports that [prisoner_nameDef], a valued member of their community, has fallen into the hands of ruthless slavers. The raider camp is heavily defended, but the captive's knowledge of pre-war technology makes them too valuable to abandon. Infiltrate the compound and extract the prisoner before they're s老旧 to the highest bidder.</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>questDescription-&gt;来自 [asker_faction_name] 的一条紧急消息：“[prisoner_nameDef] 在补给运行出现问题时被抓获。抓获他们的袭击者是一个臭名昭著的奴隶行动的一部分，该行动一直在恐吓荒原。我们不能让我们自己的人在他们手中受苦。闯入他们的要塞老旧，并将 [prisoner_nameDef] 带回家。”</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.3>任务描述-&gt;来自[asker_faction_name]的紧急通讯：一名名为[prisoner_nameDef]的幸存者在他们的商队遭到伏击后被袭击者奴役。绑架者索要巨额赎金，同时让囚犯面临难以形容的条件。唯一的选择就是直接攻击他们的防御阵地。将这个无辜的灵魂从荒地噩梦中解放出来。</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.3>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.4>questDescription-&gt;Priority alert from [asker_faction_name]: [prisoner_nameDef], a skilled wasteland survivor, has been captured by a gang of violent raiders known for their slave trading operations. The prisoner's intimate knowledge of local settlements makes them both valuable and 危险 in enemy hands. Stage a rescue mission before this information can be extracted and used against innocent communities.</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.4>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.0>任务名称-&gt;行动：救援 [prisoner_nameDef]</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.0>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.1>任务名称-&gt;废土解放：[prisoner_nameDef]</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.1>
