  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.11>任务名称-&gt;大逃亡</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.11>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.2>任务名称-&gt;打破锁链</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.2>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.3>任务名称-&gt;奴隶营渗透</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.3>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.4>任务名称-&gt;[prisoner_nameDef]的自由</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.4>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.5>questName-&gt;[prisoner_nameDef] 撤离</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.5>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.6>任务名称-&gt;袭击者营地</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.6>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.7>任务名称-&gt;解放任务：[prisoner_nameDef]</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.7>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.8>任务名称-&gt;逃出[prisoner_nameDef]</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.8>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.9>任务名称-&gt;荒原救援</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.questNameRules.rulesStrings.9>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.root.nodes.15.node.nodes.1.customLetterLabel>付款已到</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.root.nodes.15.node.nodes.1.customLetterLabel>
  <FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.root.nodes.15.node.nodes.1.customLetterText>你已经击败了战俘营！\n\n[asker_faction_name] 的付款已到。</FCP_Quest_PawnRescueHumanlike.root.nodes.15.node.nodes.1.customLetterText>
